replies.body:
I would love a Skarner Chroma Pack too. {{champion:72}} 
I have high hopes for the upcoming Chromas since Riot recently "revived" them and released a lot. But i guess from a Marketing standpoint it's true that it might not sell as well as Chroma packs for other more popular Champions like Jinx for example. {{item:3070}} 
And they seem to release chromas that are tied to skins. 
I like Skarners Skins (except for Battlecast Skarner, but that's just my opinion :P) but a Chroma pack would fit best for his Basic (Crystal-looking) Skin. Like the OP said it would be cool to have something like a Ruby-Skarner and other colors that are based on reallife Gems. 

But it's all "Supply and Demand" and maybe someday Skarner will be appreciated by the players and we can get our Chromas. And i would {{summoner:4}}  for the Riotpoints Purchase Button
